skills.description:
When Shion enters the battlefield, if more than a half of the allies are female, Shion pretends to be a female (and therefore considered a female instead of male);
increase own cri power, increase 7% crit rate and block rate for each fighter of shion's current gender (including Shion), max 28%; if only one fighter on each side when Shion enters the battle, increase 15% crit rate and block rate; During Round 1 after Shion makes his debut, he is inmune to any debuff; dispel own debuff (petrification included) for each figther of Shion's opposite sex dies on either side; recover 15% own HP for each fighter of Shion's sex dies on either side;
When fatally injured, Shion escapes to an extra dimension (which will dispel own buff and debuff) and returns upon own side's next round, recovering 50% HP and seizing all buff and 300 rage from the last enemy who attacked Shion previously. This effect can be triggered once only during each battle.

Increase own Rage recovery speed by 50%, other Ikari Team members' Rage recovery speed increase by 25%; own small skill and ULT ATK will add a layer of "Explosive Gunpowder" to the target (the effect cannot be resisted, and can be added up to 6 times); one layer of "Explosive Gunpowder" will be added when the target with "Explosive Gunpowder" attacks; 8% own HP will be restored when each layer of "Explosive Gunpowder" is added to the target; when the "Explosive Gunpowder" is detonated, an extra DMG of the target's DEF (120% + 90% x the layers of "Explosive Gunpowder") will be caused to the target, and 50% splash DMG will be caused to surrounding enemies (all detonation DMG ignores debuff). At the same time, 4% own HP will be restored when each layer of "Explosive Gunpowder" is detonated; increase own DEF by 70% and DMG by 15%; when attacked by the target with no "Explosive Gunpowder", One-man Army Ralf will be treated as having an extra 30% Anti-Crit (the effect still works even if there's no enemy with "Explosive Gunpowder");
Own debuff will be dispelled (including petrification) when One-man Army Ralf is at full Rage, and control effect is immune. The effect will last until next time One-man Army ralf releases his ULT (one round at most);
If there are at least three members of the Ikari Warriors on own side and Aid team in first round, increase own Anti-ULT by 20% for two rounds.
[Interfere Skill]: Decrease all the enemies' ATK, not stackable with other interfere skills. Interfere skill does not take effect when the target id deployed as an aid fighter.
